1. *Novom* odlukom nadležni su nametnuli nove procedire. (With the new decision, the authorities imposed new procedures.)

2. On je stigao *novom* automobilom. (He arrived in a new car.)

3. Ona će otići *novom* putem. (She will go on a new path.)

4. Prateći *novom* trendu, prodaja je porasla. (Following the new trend, sales have increased.)

5. On će se upoznati *novom* tehnologijom. (He will get acquainted with new technology.)